public interface UnaryPredicate<E>
extends java.io.Serializable

UnaryPredicate is an interface for implementing Unary testing operations. It is used for testing membership in sets of various sorts. The choice of symbol names is intended to provide signature-level compatability with Objectspace's JGL package.
